递归计算结点深度即可。

```python
class Solution:
    def solve(self, root: TreeNode, dep) -> int:
        if root == None:
            return dep
        return max(self.solve(root.left, dep+1), self.solve(root.right, dep+1))

    def maxDepth(self, root: TreeNode) -> int:
        return self.solve(root, 0)
```
